abstract: Minnesota Lynx defeat Indiana Fever, 80-77, to lead WNBA finals, 2-1.
lead_paragraph: Maya Moore made a 3-pointer at the buzzer from the top of the key to give the Minnesota Lynx an 80-77 victory over the Indiana Fever.

headline.main: Lynx’s Moore Hits 3-Pointer at Buzzer, Stunning Fever
